  "comment_text": {
    "snp1.7:11.1": "Both Norman and Bodhi add a term suggesting transgression here, in line with the commentary and the apparent sense. I don’t, as I suspect the text is corrupt. Could <i lang='pi' translate='no'>diss</i> be <i lang='pi' translate='no'>duss</i>? ",
    "snp1.7:25.4": ""
  },
